Package: upndown
Type: Package
Title: Utilities and Design Aids for Up-and-Down Dose-Finding Studies
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2025-12-30
Description: Up-and-Down (UD) is the most popular design approach for dose-finding, but it has been severely under-served by the statistical and computing communities. This is the first package that comprehensively addresses UD's needs. Development version available on Github: assaforon/upndown. Recent applied UD tutorial: Oron et al., 2022 <doi:10.1097/ALN.0000000000004282>. Recent methodological overview: Oron and Flournoy, 2024 <doi:10.51387/24-NEJSDS74>.
License: GPL-2
